{"tid":412862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「長洲覆核王」入稟高院要求法庭頒令取消何君堯議席及退回薪金","createTime":"2017-09-25T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T02:24:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":380,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fa36d36ba775566ccaae5c365c6bb3746a9fbe","tid":412862,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170925/s00001/281cf2d1d74cdaa32e296f36cfa99ce7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F281cf2d1d74cdaa32e296f36cfa99ce7.jpg&h=fbd054a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯聲稱自己是「新加坡和英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師」，近日遭到質疑，而其所屬律師行的網站昨日早上修改了何君堯的簡介，變成「獲得新加坡執業律師資格」和「獲得英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師資格」。「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅今入稟高院，要求法庭頒令取消何的議席及要求何退回薪金。<br />\n<br />\n申請人郭卓堅於入稟狀指出，答辯人立法會議員何君堯違反《選舉舞弊及非法行為》第25條，即在選舉時自稱是新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師，但經查證後發現何君堯並沒有上述國家的執業律師牌照。申請人認為何君堯利用上述名銜，謀取利益，每月收取立法會議員利益。申請人要求法庭頒令取消何的議員資格，以及何君堯須將薪酬退回。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅今在高院門外表示，由於何君堯是利用虛假聲明取得議員資格及薪金，即使上述錯誤是手民之誤，亦理應即時辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506311404678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506311404678&d=%2BEgXdx1jySSNsqNy2%2FN8WTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2284eac9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506311404678&h=aa7eb98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506311404678</a>"},{"pid":"20205054972558f3a305203e0924514752af9aa3","tid":412862,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"c0b38d1c7b7f9b46d08446a6f109f26f03b17ec6","tid":412862,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4a00662f8797983580aab630e8428dacebeddf","tid":412862,"uid":15323,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"根本就要搵人行出呢一步<br />\n全香港次次有呢d事都係得呢個長洲啊伯肯出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多d人肯去申請覆核建制班假學歷撚屌就好"},{"pid":"5a8c0f4284a44d35e29fc53a76ab86a265a147b6","tid":412862,"uid":21392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"ICAC呢"},{"pid":"54f420ea9b6af208281409b2cb800bf5c032fc2c","tid":412862,"uid":149361,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"有錢果d撚屌去撚曬邊 次次都靠個阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2e7e28f0dbf4e6b216a343ebc5b93ae61a1269","tid":412862,"uid":6192,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"希望大家會支持郭生10月1灣仔擺街站"},{"pid":"3f6669176c3cb5483e6af6fbc3d9840f7b1f408c","tid":412862,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888e6c604c534ad9654c6359eb5f4c2883fc054e","tid":412862,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"092e10b12cfe78d2a14afe5ac3db9f27a2a272c3","tid":412862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望大家會支持郭生10月1灣仔擺街站</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2d8c5383210891eb12656756e2184cff32209b","tid":412862,"uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢果d撚屌去撚曬邊 次次都靠個阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\